        </p>
        <div class="tag-row">
          <span class="tag">Final Cut Pro</span>
          <span class="tag m">Storytelling</span>
          <span class="tag g">Award-Winning</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card">
        <p class="project-num">PROJECT_04</p>
        <h3 class="project-name">Network Lab Projects</h3>
        <p class="project-desc">
          Hands-on CCNA lab exercises covering routing protocols, switching,
